lore: Strong, swift, independently intelligent and amongst the Hive Mind’s most adaptable bioforms, Tyranid Warriors are the backbone of many Tyranid invasions. Their synaptic link imbues them with advanced martial abilities, and also allows them to serve as synaptic linchpins within the wider swarms during battle.

wargear.description: Any number of models can each have their devourer replaced with one of the following:
For every 3 models in this unit, 1 model’s devourer can be replaced with 1 barbed strangler
For every 3 models in this unit, 1 model’s devourer can be replaced with 1 venom cannon.
